                     <interp inst="t18280911-303-person1668" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Bow-street officer. I saw the prisoner attempting a gentleman's pocket - I took him and searched him, and this handkerchief was found secreted in his breeches.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I picked it up on the floor, as any one might have done; I stook there for half an hour, and then the officer called and took me.</p>
